      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like he's fighting a losing battle. the more he tries to stay, the more it hurts. like, if the erasure is inevitable, isn't the pain just... unnecessary? if a character knows they're being deleted, isn't there a certain kind of relief in just letting go of the fight?",
